The '''2004 Washington State Cougars football team''' represented [[Washington State University]] in the [[college football]] [[2004 NCAA Division I-A football season|season of 2004-2005]]. The team was led by second-year head coach [[Bill Doba]], and played its home games at [[Martin Stadium]] in [[Pullman, Washington|Pullman]], [[Washington (U.S. state)|Washington]].
